summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 5975, entitled "An Ordinance providing for the improvement of Western Avenue, in the City of Seattle, from Columbia Street to Seneca Street, by repairing the foundation thereof and by replanking the same, and providing for the payment therefor by the mode of "Immediate Payment", under the provisions of ordinance number 5693 of said city, approved December 6, 1899."
